Gender Pay Gap  

On the snapshot date of 30 March 2017 there were 2,934 people employed by the Council, this is based on headcount not full-time equivalent 
numbers.  Out of these, 2,664 counted as full-pay relevant employees; 1,909 were female and 755 were male. 

 

